<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>引导博客页面</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>欢迎来到我的博客</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#about">关于我</a></li>
                <li><a href="#posts">博客文章</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">联系我</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>关于我</h2>
        <p>这是一个关于我的简短介绍。</p>
    </section>

    <section id="posts">
        <h2>博客文章</h2>
        <article>
            <h3>第一篇文章</h3>
            <p>这是第一篇博客文章的内容。</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3>第二篇文章</h3>
            <p>这是第二篇博客文章的内容。</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>联系我</h2>
        <form id="contactForm">
            <label for="name">姓名:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" required>
            <label for="email">邮箱:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" required>
            <button type="submit">发送</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 我的博客</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
